snippet.title: One Perfect Day Demo - Gamesbagus Game Jam 2022
snippet.description:
Andy doesn't know where exactly he is supposed to be, except that he is back in high school reliving that one perfect day. Over and over again.

Music & Sounds: Epidemicsound, Chosin, Zapsplat
